Name: app_length
Lemma: forall (l l' : list A), length (l++l') = length l + length l'

Name: app_assoc
Lemma: forall (l m n:list A) : l ++ m ++ n = (l ++ m) ++ n

Name: in_app_or
Lemma: forall (l m:list A) (a:A), In a (l ++ m) -> In a l \/ In a m

Name: in_or_app
Lemma: forall (l m:list A) (a:A), In a l \/ In a m -> In a (l ++ m)

Name: map_length
Lemma: forall l, length (map l) = length l

Name: rev_app_distr
Lemma: forall x y:list A, rev (x ++ y) = rev y ++ rev x

Name: rev_length
Lemma: forall l, length (rev l) = length l

Name: firstn_all
Lemma: forall l, firstn (length l) l = l

Name: firstn_skipn
Lemma: forall n l, firstn n l ++ skipn n l = l

Name: Add_app
Lemma: forall a l1 l2, Add a (l1++l2) (l1++a::l2)

Name: app_eq_nil
Lemma: forall (l l':list A) : l ++ l' = [] -> l = [] /\ l' = []

Name: skipn_all
Lemma: forall l, skipn (length l) l = nil
